title: Nextbase DVR122 Dash Cam
description: The Nextbase 122 is the fully established entry-level Dash Cam ideal for the younger or first time driver. With 720p HD recording, on a 5 layered glass lens it provides the perfect picture for day-time driving. The 122 uses a bright and clear 2-inch high resolution screen for easy menu selection and playback. Intelligent Parking Mode protects your vehicle when parked by recording any bump or physical movement when the vehicle is left unattended. It fits neatly onto the vehicle using the patented Click&Go PRO car mount. With integrated magnetic powered connectors and a strong adhesive seal, it's the ideal mounting solution. Nextbase offers a free cloud video storage solution online for up to 30 days using mynextbase.com

title: APEMAN Dash Cam C420D
description: Dual Lens, No More Fear Rear Collisions - C420D Dash Cam is like two cameras for the price of one. SHARP FULL HD resolution and dual 170° ultra wide angle lenses provide outstanding image quality with a broader field of vision. Superior 1080p@30fps Video & Night Vision - You are always under protection with the Full HD front view and 720P HD rear view. With Advanced Starvis Sensor, WDR technology and F1.8 Large Aperture, the dashcam captures finest details even in low light conditions.

title: YADA 720P HD Roadcam
description: Record the road ahead or keep your car secure when parked with this Yada Roadcam dash camera. The 720p HD resolution delivers ultra-clear viewing so you see everything, and the 2-inch LCD lets you replay events after they happen for immediate review. G-sensor activated technology automatically saves videos of break-in attempts and door dings. With a compact, discreet design, this Yada Road Cam dash camera mounts easily on your windshield without getting in the way.

title: APEMAN Dash Cam 1080P
description: 1080P FULL HD FULL HD DASH CAM - Simultaneous recording with super high resolution 1080P lens, and large 3 inch LCD screen. It can offer clearer videos and images and reproduces the key moment even when driving at high speed. 170° SUPER WIDE ANGLE - This car recorder employs 170° super wide angle lens. The ultra-wide field of view reduces blind spots and captures more details to preserve the real scene. BUILT-IN G-SENSOR - With the built-in G-sensor, Apeman car cam can automatically detect sudden shake/collision and lock the footage to prevent the video from being overwritten even in loop recording. The accident scene can be restored.

title: Nextbase 222 Dash Cam
description: The Nextbase 222 Dash Cam offers full HD, with an improved chipset to record in full 1080p HD for enhanced day and night time footage. It uses an enhanced 6G lens and 140 viewing angle to capture the road ahead in greater detail. The 222 uses a brand new compact design, with a clear 2.5-inch HD IPS panel for a user-friendly experience. Intelligent Parking Mode protects your vehicle when parked by recording any bump or physical movement when the vehicle is left unattended. The exclusive new Click&Go Pro mount features a low profile design and high strength neodymium magnets for easy installation and removal from your Dash Cam with just one hand. It uses a high-strength strong adhesive seal to provide the perfect mounting solution.
